RESTAURANT NAME AND MENU ITEMS GENERATOR USING OPENAI AND LANGCHAIN
路Designed and implemented an Al-driven application to generate creative and contextually relevant restaurant names and cuisine types based on user preferences.
路Utilized LangChain to create prompt chains and manage conversationalmemory for iterative refinement of outputs.
路Developed a user-friendly interface using Streamlit,enabling interactive input and real-time feedback for personalized recommendations.
路Technologies:OpenAl API,LangChain,Python,Streamlit.

